metadata.name: Mad Eagle Club 2.0 #1
metadata.description: Mad Eagle Club 2.0 is a collection of 10,500 unique NFTs that live on Ethereum. The Mad Eagles came from BNB Chain and now invading the Ethereum universe to take over the NFT world that make the Mad Eagles unique and superior. The Mad Eagles have undergone a genetic evolution carefully executed by a scientist called Uranus who will continue to gradually improve the evolutionary genes of the Eagles for limitless possibilities.
